    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to level 1 per MRL 2 guidance and documented as not-assessed with justification. Hemolysis index prediction error (max 11.4%) is within the ±15% acceptance criterion across the full CPB operating envelope. The computational model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Assessment accepted under ProfileMinimal pending full registry COU linkage.",
